VALUES
  ('social-worker-moex-02011', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-d2552697', 'sub-social-worker-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '為協助家庭照顧兒童減輕父母育兒負擔，並執行行政院 104 年所核定修正之「父母未就業家庭育兒津貼 實施計畫」，補助民眾育兒津貼，衛生福利部特訂定「父母未就業家庭育兒津貼申領作業要點」，有關 補助金額內容，下列何者錯誤？', '["低收入戶每名兒童每月補助新臺幣5千元", "中低收入戶每名兒童每月補助新臺幣4千元", "兒童之父母（監護人）經稅捐稽徵機關核定之最近 1 年之綜合所得總額，合計未達申報標準或綜合所 得稅率未達百分之二十者，每名兒童每月補助新臺幣3千元", "本津貼以月為核算單位，補助至兒童滿二足歲當月止"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5659ee27e44f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7fe5f1f09f6b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會政策與社會立法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02012', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-d2552697', 'sub-social-worker-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據特殊境遇家庭扶助條例，特殊境遇家庭扶助包括緊急生活扶助、子女生活津貼、子女教育補助等項 目。有關申請緊急生活扶助者的條文內容，下列何者錯誤？', '["按當年度低收入戶每人每月最低生活費用標準一倍核發", "每人每次以補助3個月為原則", "同一個案同一事由以補助一次為限", "申請緊急生活扶助應於事實發生後 3 個月內，檢具相關文件資料向戶籍所在地直轄市、縣（市）主管 機關申請"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5659ee27e44f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7fe5f1f09f6b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會政策與社會立法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02013', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-d2552697', 'sub-social-worker-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '提出通往奴役之路（Road to Serfdom）概念的學者是：', '["Milton Friedman", "Friedrich Hayek", "Adam Smith", "Joseph Alois Schumpeter"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5659ee27e44f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7fe5f1f09f6b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會政策與社會立法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02014', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-d2552697', 'sub-social-worker-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '為了使家庭及受僱勞工減輕育兒的經濟負擔，政府提供民眾不同的福利措施。下列那一項是屬於財稅福 利？', '["幼兒教育券", "幼兒學前特別扣除額", "保母托育補助", "父母未就業家庭育兒津貼"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5659ee27e44f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7fe5f1f09f6b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會政策與社會立法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02015', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-d2552697', 'sub-social-worker-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '1989 年為了讓「兒童權利宣言」能具備拘束力，聯合國大會乃通過「兒童權利公約」對各締約國具有法 令的約束力。該公約提出四項普遍性的指導原則，下列何者錯誤？', '["禁止歧視原則", "兒童最佳利益", "生存與發展權", "福利與受教權"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5659ee27e44f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7fe5f1f09f6b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會政策與社會立法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02016', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-d2552697', 'sub-social-worker-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '依照全民健康保險法的條文內容，本保險財務，由保險人至少每多少年精算一次，每次精算25年？', '["3年", "4年", "5年", "6年"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5659ee27e44f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7fe5f1f09f6b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會政策與社會立法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02017', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-d2552697', 'sub-social-worker-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '依國民年金法規定，保險人為辦理本保險所需之人事及行政管理經費，以當年度應收保險費總額之百分 之多少為上限，由中央主管機關負擔？', '["百分之一點五", "百分之三點五", "百分之五點五", "百分之六點五"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5659ee27e44f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7fe5f1f09f6b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會政策與社會立法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02018', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-107-d2552697', 'sub-social-worker-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列選項中，那一個組合是屬於兒童及少年福利與權益保障法中之兒少福利機構？①托嬰中心  ②幼兒', '["早期療育機構", "安置及教養機構  ⑤心理輔導或家庭諮詢機構", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5659ee27e44f", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7fe5f1f09f6b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107030", "c": "107", "s": "0604", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會政策與社會立法", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02019', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-106-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'essay', '請詳述成為遊民之歷程及原因為何？遊民可能導致那些問題？並請以人權與增權
